Name: I-DOCK RESTAURANT
Review Text: Good dinner with burger and beer. The hamburger is good, but the steak was too nervy and chewy. In reception they say that lockdown at 20, but at 19,20 the restaurant doesn't allow you to seat to eat. Bah...

Name: I-DOCK RESTAURANT
Review Text: We stayed at the hotel Room Mate Aitana and had dinner at their restaurant I - dock. Very nice hotel and restaurant! We ordered  The spaghett agilloi with prawns, breaded whitefish (I think was flounder) with green mint tea and a kids meal ‚Ä¶

Name: I-DOCK RESTAURANT
Review Text: Great place to chill at the dock terrace or inside in a stylish modern decoration. Just a stone away from the Central Station to enjoy a walk next to the water until you reach I Dock. Not crowded as it‚Äôs not in the center. Good cava and delicious food. I recommend the oyster mushrooms bitterballen and the BBQ octopus.

Name: I-DOCK RESTAURANT

Name: I-DOCK RESTAURANT
